name: DogZos #Discord Edition
description:
To help the growth of the community and celebrate the launch of the discord, i have decided to do this special 100/100 edition priced at 0.25 TEZ that will give FIVE DIFFERENT people the chance to chose ONE new DogZos. You will be able to chose your favorite color and will be airdropped the DogZos throughout the 500 editions. You can buy more than one edition to improve your chances but you can only win ONE time.

Feel Free to join us on Twitter or Discord ! :)
